# File Navigation Guide

## Core Directories
- `/src/app` - Next.js app router pages and layouts
- `/src/components` - React components
- `/src/hooks` - Custom React hooks
- `/src/services` - API services
- `/src/types` - TypeScript type definitions
- `/src/utils` - Utility functions
- `/public` - Static assets

## Main Section Components
Each main section of the portfolio has its component structure:

### Hero Section
- [src/components/Hero.tsx](mdc:src/components/Hero.tsx) - Main component

### About Section
- [src/components/About.tsx](mdc:src/components/About.tsx) - Main component
- [src/components/About/](mdc:src/components/About/) - Subcomponents

### Projects Section
- [src/components/Projects.tsx](mdc:src/components/Projects.tsx) - Main component
- [src/components/Projects/](mdc:src/components/Projects/) - Subcomponents
- [src/hooks/useGitHubProjects.ts](mdc:src/hooks/useGitHubProjects.ts) - GitHub projects data

### Experience Section
- [src/components/Experience.tsx](mdc:src/components/Experience.tsx) - Main component
- [src/components/Experience/](mdc:src/components/Experience/) - Subcomponents

### Contact Section
